txt.en: Defeat crawlers in the Towers of the Teeth ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
There is much to be done in the Towers of the Teeth.
Enter the Towers of the Teeth
Crawlers have made a home for themselves beneath the Towers of the Teeth. Defeating some of them may make passage through these dark corridors safer for those who brave these depths.
The Towers of the Teeth are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should defeat crawlers in the Towers of the Teeth.
The Towers of the Teeth are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should defeat crawlers in the Towers of the Teeth.
You have defeated many crawlers lurking within the Towers of the Teeth. Your efforts will be felt by those who venture below the Towers.
